
Pds (Pardus Desktop Services)
-----------------------------
Pardus Desktop Services provides some methods to develop cross desktop 
environment applications with Qt and Kde libs.

It supports following Desktop Environments:

- Kde 4
- Kde 3.5
- Xfce 4

**Howto**
::

 >> import pds
 >> instance = pds.Pds()
 >> instance.session.Name
 'kde'
 >> instance.session.Version
 '4'
 >> instance.home
 '/home/pars'
 >> instance.install_prefix
 '/usr/pars/4'
 >> instance.config_file
 '/home/pars/.kde4/share/config/kdeglobals'
 >> instance.config_path
 '/home/pars/.kde4/'
